div.summary:
The Episcopal Methodist Church recently announced their appointments. The
                    following men received local appointments: E. F. Busey, presiding elder of the
                    Rockingham district; Staunton--J. L. Clark; Augusta--W. R. Stringer;
                    Churchville--A. A. P. Neall, E. Crickenberger, W. H. Rippetoe, supernumerary;
                    Fairfield--William McDonald; and Mt. Sidney--J. J. Engle.
